OL,3,CAirlines with low-cost reputations
OL,4,C'not always cheapest because of extras'
OL,6,FResearchers conducted a snapshot price
OL,7,Fanalysis for the cheapest return
OL,8,Fflights from London airports to
OL,9,FMalaga, Athens and Naples with
OL,10,FRyanair, Wizz Air, British Airways,
OL,11,FJet2 and easyJet booked in December
OL,12,F2023 for travel on weekends this month.
OL,14,FThey included the price of taking a
OL,15,Fcabin bag as hand luggage.
OL,17,FThe cost of seat selection was added
OL,18,Ffor Ryanair and Wizz Air as a previous
OL,19,Fsurvey indicated they are the airlines
OL,20,Fleast likely to automatically seat
OL,21,Ftravel companions together.
