OL,3,CAirlines with low-cost reputations
OL,4,C'not always cheapest because of extras'
OL,6,FThe study found that while budget
OL,7,Fairlines often had the cheapest
OL,8,Fheadline fares, Ryanair and Wizz Air
OL,9,Ffailed to return the lowest price on
OL,10,Fany occasion when the cost of a cabin
OL,11,Fbag and seat selection ` always
OL,12,Fincluded in British Airways and Jet2
OL,13,Ffares ` were taken into account.
OL,15,FBritish Airways was found to have the
OL,16,Flowest total price for Naples flights,
OL,17,Fat #120.
OL,19,FThat compares with #198 with Jet2,
OL,20,F#185 with Wizz Air, #132 with Ryanair
OL,21,Fand #126 with easyJet.
