OL,3,CAirlines with low-cost reputations
OL,4,C'not always cheapest because of extras'
OL,6,FBritish Airways was the second
OL,7,Fcheapest airline, behind easyJet, for
OL,8,FMalaga flights, but the most expensive
OL,9,Ffor trips to Athens.
OL,11,FBaggage and seat selection accounted
OL,12,Ffor an average of #113 across the
OL,13,Fthree routes with Wizz Air, #57 with
OL,14,FRyanair and #52 with easyJet.
OL,16,FWizz Air's cabin bag fee includes
OL,17,Fpriority boarding.
