OL,4,C'not always cheapest because of extras'
OL,6,F"But if you want to sit next to your
OL,7,Fkids or take more than a few items of
OL,8,Fclothes with you, then you'll
OL,9,Fincreasingly find better prices
OL,10,Felsewhere.
OL,12,F"Next time you're booking a flight,
OL,13,Flook beyond the headline fare and
OL,14,Ffactor in the cost of extras you need,
OL,15,Fbefore you book."
OL,17,FA Ryanair spokesman said: "This is
OL,18,Fmore fake news from Which?.
